      "versionNonce": 4,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• Unidirectional data flow: state flows down, user actions flow up\n• Repositories coordinate local and remote data sources\n• UI is driven from persistent local models whenever possible\n• Single-activity app with Fragment / Compose-based feature screens",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• Unidirectional data flow: state flows down, user actions flow up\n• Repositories coordinate local and remote data sources\n• UI is driven from persistent local models whenever possible\n• Single-activity app with Fragment / Compose-based feature screens",
      "lineHeight": 1.4,
      "baseline": 10
    },
